window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Loki and I are worlds apart.</p> <p>The Ice God, my brutal ex-mate, is rewriting my memory, my desire, and my very soul. When he’s done, I won’t be Tessa Morrigan. </p> <p>I hold no illusion that Loki will come for me. He doesn’t even know I’ve been torn from him, and he’s now with an imposter. </p> <p>I’m being replaced and forgotten. </p> <p>When all hope dies, a flame sparks to life within me. </p> <p>I’m doing everything in my power to hide my unborn son, but he’s more than eager to show me that he has enough magic to protect his mommy and tear apart the immortal enemy who has caged us.</p>"; 
